title: Driver narrowly avoids being crushed by a cement mixer rolling over
text:
Share Driver narrowly avoids being crushed by a cement mixer rolling over 
Several Melbourne drivers were lucky to escape unscathed after a cement mixer rolled onto its side after taking a corner too fast. 
The driver in the Ford Territory and the owner of the dashcam that filmed the encounter last year could only watch on as the top heavy truck lost traction and came rolling to them. 
The driver of the cement truck was lucky to escape without major injury. Most Viewed
